You can find the Textadept editor homepage at https://foicica.com/textadept/index.html.

To see how to use EditorConfig check http://editorconfig.org.

To enable this module:
  cd ~/.textadept
  mkdir -p modules/textadept/editing
  cp /path/to/editorconfig.lua modules/textadept/editing
  echo "require(\"textadept.editing.editorconfig\").enable()" >> init.lua
